                        <interp inst="t18480821-name-215" type="surname" value="RUSSETT"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480821-name-215" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH RUSSETT</persName>
                  </hi>. I was at Mr. Smith's when the prisoner came on 17th July—I asked to look at the shilling—Mrs. Smith passed it to m, an before I could scarcely look at it, the prisoner endeavoured to get it from me, but she did not—I gave it to Mrs. Smith.</p>
